步健全内部管理制度，提高审核把关能力。防止存在刻意通过拜金、炫富、炫权、享乐等制造爽点，对主题的把握和主角的塑造偏离主流价值导向，以及宣扬不劳而获、一步登天、一夜暴富的人生观、价值观等问题的微短剧上线播出。 广电总局出手整治「霸总」微短剧，防止通过拜金、炫富等制造爽点 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/70/v2-85319926503bf0707cb82600bf20e4b8_1440w.avis?source=172ae18b&biz_tag=Post"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "27 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/5132686750"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI5bjMsuKcxKMOEAMaCTExMjAwMzE4MyDC1pK6BjAAONMIQAhyCjUxMzI2ODY3NTB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1732668820.81626", "card_id": "Q_5187112862", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 506}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "华为 Mate 70 系列正式发布，余承东称「靠抄袭没有未来」，华为做了哪些创新？这一系列竞争力如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "11 月 26 日，余承东在发布会上表示，Mate 一直引领工艺的创新，不断创新才能引领行业，靠抄袭是没有未来的。 余承东强调，Mate 一直被模仿从未被超越，能超越 Mate 的只有 Mate。 据了解，Mate 70 是华为第一款首发搭载纯血鸿蒙的手机。华为 Mate70 系列正式发布华为 Mate70/Pro/Pro+ 系列旗舰手机亮相 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-cd55ff25b8f4a3a42f696d681856dd9f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "19 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/5187112862"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI5bjMsuKcxKMOEAMaCTExMjAxMzk1NiCT5JW6BjAAOLUGQAlyCjUxODcxMTI4NjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1732668820.82200", "card_id": "Q_883251623", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 2024ICPC 昆明区域赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg